abstract: President Obama will attend Carrier Classic, which will pit North Carolina against Michigan State in first college basketball game to take place on an active aircraft carrier.
snippet: President Obama will attend the Carrier Classic game on the aircraft carrier that buried Osama bin Laden at sea.
lead_paragraph: President Obama will attend the Carrier Classic game on the aircraft carrier that buried Osama bin Laden at sea.
